import { Tabs, TabItem } from '$lib/mdx';

Os repositórios oferecem armazenamento de entidades tipadas com validação de schema.

---

## Criar Entidade

### POST /api/v1/repositories/\{repositoryId\}

Cria uma nova entidade no repositório.

**Request:**
```json
{
  "data": {
    "name": "Acme Corp",
    "industry": "Technology",
    "employeeCount": 500
  }
}
```

**Response (201 Created):**
```json
{
  "id": "ent_abc123",
  "data": {
    "name": "Acme Corp",
    "industry": "Technology",
    "employeeCount": 500
  },
  "createdAt": "2024-01-15T10:00:00Z",
  "updatedAt": "2024-01-15T10:00:00Z"
}
```

---

## Listar Entidades

### GET /api/v1/repositories/\{repositoryId\}

Lista todas as entidades com paginação.

**Parâmetros de Query:**

| Parâmetro | Tipo | Padrão | Descrição |
|-----------|------|---------|-------------|
| `limit` | integer | 20 | Máximo de itens a retornar |
| `cursor` | string | null | Cursor de paginação |

**Response (200 OK):**
```json
{
  "entities": [
    {
      "id": "ent_abc123",
      "data": { "name": "Acme Corp" },
      "createdAt": "2024-01-15T10:00:00Z",
      "updatedAt": "2024-01-15T10:00:00Z"
    }
  ],
  "nextCursor": "eyJsYXN0S2V5Ijo...",
  "totalCount": 150
}
```

---

## Obter Entidade

### GET /api/v1/repositories/\{repositoryId\}/\{entityId\}

Obtém uma entidade por ID.

**Response (200 OK):**
```json
{
  "id": "ent_abc123",
  "data": {
    "name": "Acme Corp",
    "industry": "Technology"
  },
  "createdAt": "2024-01-15T10:00:00Z",
  "updatedAt": "2024-01-15T10:30:00Z"
}
```

---

## Atualizar Entidade

### PUT /api/v1/repositories/\{repositoryId\}/\{entityId\}

Atualiza uma entidade existente.

**Request:**
```json
{
  "data": {
    "name": "Acme Corporation",
    "industry": "Technology",
    "employeeCount": 600
  }
}
```

**Response (200 OK):** Retorna a entidade atualizada.

---

## Excluir Entidade

### DELETE /api/v1/repositories/\{repositoryId\}/\{entityId\}

Exclui uma entidade.

**Response (204 No Content):** Corpo vazio em caso de sucesso.

---

## Consultar Entidades

### POST /api/v1/repositories/\{repositoryId\}/query

Consulta entidades com filtro opcional.

**Request:**
```json
{
  "filter": "industry = :industry",
  "filterValues": {
    ":industry": "Technology"
  },
  "limit": 20,
  "cursor": null,
  "sortBy": "createdAt",
  "sortOrder": "desc"
}
```

**Response (200 OK):** Mesmo formato da resposta de listagem de entidades.

---

## Exemplos de Código

<Tabs items={[{"label":"C# SDK","content":"<pre><code class=\"language-csharp\">    // Define entity\n    public record Customer : EntityBase\n    {\n        public required string Name { get; init; }\n        public required string Email { get; init; }\n        public string? Phone { get; init; }\n        public CustomerTier Tier { get; init; } = CustomerTier.Standard;\n    }\n\n    public enum CustomerTier\n    {\n        Standard,\n        Premium,\n        Enterprise\n    }\n\n    // Get repository reference\n    var customers = client.GetRepository&lt;Customer&gt;(&quot;repo_customers&quot;);\n\n    // Create entity\n    var customer = new Customer\n    {\n        Id = Guid.NewGuid().ToString(),\n        Name = &quot;Acme Corp&quot;,\n        Email = &quot;contact@acme.com&quot;,\n        Tier = CustomerTier.Premium\n    };\n\n    var createResult = await customers.CreateAsync(customer);\n\n    // Get entity\n    var getResult = await customers.GetAsync(customer.Id);\n\n    // Update entity\n    var updatedCustomer = customer with { Tier = CustomerTier.Enterprise };\n    var updateResult = await customers.UpdateAsync(updatedCustomer);\n\n    // Delete entity\n    var deleteResult = await customers.DeleteAsync(customer.Id);\n\n    // List entities\n    var listResult = await customers.ListAsync(new PaginationOptions { Limit = 50 });\n\n    // Query entities\n    var filter = new QueryFilter { PartitionKey = customer.Id };\n    var queryResult = await customers.QueryAsync(filter);\n\n    // Check existence\n    var existsResult = await customers.ExistsAsync(customer.Id);\n    if (existsResult.IsSuccess &amp;&amp; existsResult.Value)\n    {\n        Console.WriteLine(&quot;Customer exists&quot;);\n    }\n</code></pre>"},{"label":"cURL","content":"<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">    # Create entity\n    curl -X POST &quot;https://api.terrascale.io/api/v1/repositories/repo_customers&quot; \\\n      -H &quot;Authorization: Bearer ts_live_your_api_key&quot; \\\n      -H &quot;Content-Type: application/json&quot; \\\n      -d &#39;{\n        &quot;data&quot;: {\n          &quot;name&quot;: &quot;Acme Corp&quot;,\n          &quot;email&quot;: &quot;contact@acme.com&quot;,\n          &quot;tier&quot;: &quot;Premium&quot;\n        }\n      }&#39;\n\n    # Get entity\n    curl &quot;https://api.terrascale.io/api/v1/repositories/repo_customers/ent_abc123&quot; \\\n      -H &quot;Authorization: Bearer ts_live_your_api_key&quot;\n\n    # Update entity\n    curl -X PUT &quot;https://api.terrascale.io/api/v1/repositories/repo_customers/ent_abc123&quot; \\\n      -H &quot;Authorization: Bearer ts_live_your_api_key&quot; \\\n      -H &quot;Content-Type: application/json&quot; \\\n      -d &#39;{\n        &quot;data&quot;: {\n          &quot;name&quot;: &quot;Acme Corporation&quot;,\n          &quot;email&quot;: &quot;contact@acme.com&quot;,\n          &quot;tier&quot;: &quot;Enterprise&quot;\n        }\n      }&#39;\n\n    # Delete entity\n    curl -X DELETE &quot;https://api.terrascale.io/api/v1/repositories/repo_customers/ent_abc123&quot; \\\n      -H &quot;Authorization: Bearer ts_live_your_api_key&quot;\n\n    # Query entities\n    curl -X POST &quot;https://api.terrascale.io/api/v1/repositories/repo_customers/query&quot; \\\n      -H &quot;Authorization: Bearer ts_live_your_api_key&quot; \\\n      -H &quot;Content-Type: application/json&quot; \\\n      -d &#39;{\n        &quot;filter&quot;: &quot;tier = :tier&quot;,\n        &quot;filterValues&quot;: { &quot;:tier&quot;: &quot;Enterprise&quot; }\n      }&#39;\n</code></pre>"}]} />

